<h1>This website was created with art in the public domain.</h1>

<p>All stories and poems by Edgar Allan Poe are in the public domain because he died under mysterious circumstances over 100 years ago.</p>
<p>All art used on this site was sourced from Wikimedia Commons, a media file repository which makes public domain and freely-licensed 
educational media content available to everyone.</p>
<p>The artists whose work was used on this site are Gustave Doré, Édouard Manet, William Heath Robinson, Odilon Redon, John R. Neill, and William Thomas Horton.
We thank them for their interpretations of Poe's work.</p>

